---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout locale="en" title="OK Hosting">
  <section class="project-hero">
    <video class="hero-video" autoplay loop muted playsinline><source src="/projects/okhosting/screens/OKHo.mp4" type="video/mp4"/></video>
    <div class="hero-overlay" style="background:rgba(0,0,0,0.55);backdrop-filter:blur(4px);-webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(4px)"></div>
    <div class="container"><div class="hero-content">
      <a href="/#results" class="back-link"><svg width="20" height="20" viewBox="0 0 20 20" fill="none"><path d="M15 5L5 10L15 15" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"/></svg>Back</a>
      <h1 class="project-title">OK HOSTING</h1><p class="project-tagline">From hosting provider to technology brand</p><p class="project-context">Technology / Hosting / IT — Mexico</p>
    </div></div>
  </section>
  <section class="project-section"><div class="container"><span class="section-label-text"><i>01</i> Problem</span><p class="project-body">OK Hosting was perceived as a commodity hosting provider. It needed to reposition as a technology company offering hosting, software, IT management, cybersecurity and AI, competing against Neubox and Xpress. Their site hadn't had a real overhaul in 8 years.</p></div></section>
  <section class="project-section-alt"><div class="container"><span class="section-label-text"><i>02</i> System & Approach</span><p class="project-body">Complete rebranding: new brand identity, website design, UX/UI process. Competitive benchmark, user personas (Rodrigo Sánchez, Mexican tech entrepreneur), restructured information architecture for IT service conversion.</p><div class="project-approach"><h4>Approach</h4><p>Competitive benchmark, user personas, reorganized architecture, bold new visual identity, IT-service-oriented website.</p></div></div></section>
  <section class="project-gallery"><div class="container"><img src="/projects/okhosting/screens/brand.webp" alt="Brand"/><img src="/projects/okhosting/screens/mockuMagazine.webp" alt="Mockup" class="mt-4"/></div></section>
  <section class="project-section"><div class="container"><span class="section-label-text"><i>03</i> Website</span><img src="/projects/okhosting/screens/OkHosting-Screen2.webp" alt="Screen" class="mt-4"/><img src="/projects/okhosting/screens/OkHosting-Screen3.webp" alt="Screen" class="mt-4"/></div></section>
  <section class="project-result"><div class="container"><div class="result-box"><h2>Result</h2><p>A memorable identity positioning OK Hosting as a full-spectrum technology company. Full redesign with estimated 40-60% improvement in perceived speed. Reduction in support tickets from user confusion.</p></div></div></section>
</BaseLayout>